        "share_text": "GIG GUIDE\nWe\u00e2\u0080\u0099re gearing up for yet another big weekend at The Oak!\n\nFRIDAY\nThe newest instalment of Bloakes At The Oak with @benjaminfrasermckenzie joined by @auntyalan.wav. Joker Draw sits at $9900\n\nSATURDAY\n@nunchukkasuperfly return for another show for their \"of you go down, i go down too\" EP Launch with @_laurapanicband \nAFL Grand Final being shown of the Big screen in the Sports Lounge\n\nSUNDAY\nThe Oak Seafood Lunch, 4 Course Seafood special curated by @josh_cale_nicholson $69pp, Link in Bio for bookings\nTo go along with our lunch we\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve got @huntervalleyramblers last Residency Gig\n\nVINYLS\n@just.bonnie.anne, @mistahdux & @pc___dysco will be turning tables and heads all weekend! \n\nLive.Local.Free #ROAK",
